{"tid":1275200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家，唔想再有人犧牲，暴力係解決唔到問題","createTime":"2019-07-01T18:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T20:44:31.000Z","uid":123954,"like":3,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1efcbc194cd6e06c27e491a62eabde8354735599","tid":1275200,"uid":123954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"平心而論，今日得到咗啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n得到既只係我地依然不割蓆，搞到民陣急急腳發聲明將責任推落政府到；搞到記者朋友急急腳post所有正面信息（包括貼「不要破壞」提示，拎野飲擺低錢）去挽回大家嘅形象。<br />\n<br />\n選擇衝擊嘅你呢？下次繼續衝，繼續升級。<br />\n<br />\n我已經陸續見到多次參與遊行嘅fb，而家怪大家衝，搞到冇晒動力。我唔係想分化、割蓆，而係衝擊嘅行為先真正分化緊大家、消磨緊大家意志。<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅朋友，我知我講野冇咩說服力，求下你地認真思考下訴諸暴力到底有咩得著？我知你地好偉大好勇敢，既然連死都唔怕，唔好怕生存，只要你地仲起我地身邊，我地一定可以諗到更好對策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6fa0a6f0e5f18bc823108ba60c70a09cf472cff6","tid":1275200,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"暴力解決唔到問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依句你同D狗講呀</span>"},{"pid":"f96da1e0c42c3e2e48cb8d6bcf28d9e7e97a954e","tid":1275200,"uid":147317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:39:12.000Z","msg":"今日有人行動又有宣言<br />\n你票説服你身邊既人而非去攻擊幫你衝既人<br />\n我發夢見到今日其實係做得好好"},{"pid":"e892665fd0b03661e69a9a23d2d7f0a51fb11a60","tid":1275200,"uid":123954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fa0a6f0e5f18bc823108ba60c70a09cf472cff6","tid":1275200,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"暴力解決唔到問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依句你同D狗講呀</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"做乜要將自己同隻狗比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人類唔怕獅子老虎係靠個腦，唔係靠打交"},{"pid":"1991985b434787e96f9ad776dcc9264947502ed9","tid":1275200,"uid":91192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"衝擊就消磨<br />\n鳩坐就唔消磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabb678448b84ad156ce49442355c98b4defe9f5","tid":1275200,"uid":123954,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1991985b434787e96f9ad776dcc9264947502ed9","tid":1275200,"uid":91192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:43:07.000Z","msg":"衝擊就消磨<br />\n鳩坐就唔消磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:52:02.000Z","msg":"我唔支持佔領嘅，因為真係消磨兼民怨。<br />\n<br />\n與其日日/隔幾日出去佔/衝，倒不如佢推一次就遊一次，養精蓄銳，103萬，200萬01，300萬，400萬...<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得我太理想化，但我仍相信靠我地團結去遊行加上政府嘅漠視係可以爭取到民意。"},{"pid":"ee2bb9038d7d3716eb3bec8dba53313a16df2d93","tid":1275200,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:14:18.000Z","msg":"請你如何界定暴力的定，他們有傷害過任何一位市民嗎，他們只一班絕望的人士，想以佔領立法會向林鄭控訴。"},{"pid":"8c2402f63462b14cd6bd966ab3b66e30ad3bc594","tid":1275200,"uid":45957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:15:42.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦 今日唔衝擊 只會好似69 616咁遊撚完返屋企咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ed0c94c6b201be5df90b509613e8b19ac74762","tid":1275200,"uid":249965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2402f63462b14cd6bd966ab3b66e30ad3bc594","tid":1275200,"uid":45957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:15:42.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦 今日唔衝擊 只會好似69 616咁遊撚完返屋企咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:26:42.000Z","msg":"今日你冇返屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4775c1b